/>\n<br />\n如是者，假如我們希望社會能夠寬容地看待被論定為「暴動」的「暴徒」，理解這些無聲者的訴求，接納這些無權者的諫言，我想，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我們必須警惕每一言一行，到底會更接近目標，還是距離更遠呢？</strong></span>"},{"pid":"0e1b52877a9836702cb0efcad8ec14fa755230f6","tid":1414681,"uid":115977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:23:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我要各位手足<br />\n不流血！不受傷！不被捕！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a9229f2d21deacd2d94b4154c0c28f922c236201","tid":1414681,"uid":156791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:28:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cfad088d6dec0f1c265645ebce2620927c42322b","tid":1414681,"uid":52194,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:29:47.000Z","msg":"都係嗰句啦<br />\n火唔好亂玩<br />\n睇住燒到自己<br />\n小心啊"},{"pid":"722183388aae5243f62c9d9aedb3a3c1da566321","tid":1414681,"uid":297356,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b6434c6f562cdb72ec799d05e6c0a2a8e82ecfe2","tid":1414681,"uid":101226,"like":57,"dislike":231,"score":-174,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:42:21.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 無黑警係無辜㗎屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:30:41.000Z","msg":"成本高效益低 不如去機場集會好過"},{"pid":"62dc3b10df70de23cbdd9c87eb3bd4603e1bd992","tid":1414681,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:31:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3884619dabffcc129ce19cce76c7d3a3b70be2e2","tid":1414681,"uid":134054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:32:27.000Z","msg":"知道前線好大壓力 要贏<br />\n不過真係要對準政權 就算啲藍絲/on9 C9講野刻薄 都係屌走佢算 唔好郁手<br />\n<br />\n利申 佢地郁手先可以還拖 但唔打死佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"2f12c2f014eb1269c7b65d3cd7b31e02ebe01a36","tid":1414681,"uid":2036,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:33:02.000Z","msg":"唔好spin 狗同狗屋/ 火方向 <br />\n唔好俾政府帶動每日洗腦<br />\n示威阻人影響經濟<br />\n<br />\n